languages.text: "Видишь эти трупы? Хорошие парни и девки поплатились из-за моей ненасытности. И твоей лжи. Мы оба примем кару Императора, готовься!"

traits.locale_text: "Видишь эти трупы? Хорошие парни и девки поплатились из-за моей ненасытности. И твоей лжи. Мы оба примем кару Императора, готовься!"

languages.text: "You see these corpses? These fine lads and lasses paid the price for my greed. And for your lies. We'll both be receiving the Emperor's punishment, of that you can be certain!"
languages.original_text: "Видишь эти трупы? Хорошие парни и девки поплатились из-за моей ненасытности. И твоей лжи. Мы оба примем кару Императора, готовься!"

"You see the corpses? These fine lads and lassies paid for my greediness. And your lies. We both will accept the Emperor's punishment, so get ready!"

languages.text: 「この死体の山が見えるか？気の良いこいつらは、俺の欲の代償を払ってくれたんだ。そして、お前が吐いた嘘の犠牲になった。俺たちはお互い、皇帝の罰を受けるべきなんだよ！」
languages.original_text: "You see these corpses? These fine lads and lasses paid the price for my greed. And for your lies. We'll both be receiving the Emperor's punishment, of that you can be certain!"

traits.locale_text: 「この死体の山が見えるか？気の良いこいつらは、俺の欲の代償を払ってくれたんだ。そして、お前が吐いた嘘の犠牲になった。俺たちはお互い、皇帝の罰を受けるべきなんだよ！」

languages.text: «¿Ves estos cadáveres? Estos muchachos y muchachas han pagado el precio de mi avaricia. Y el de tus mentiras. A los dos nos llegará el castigo del Emperador, ¡eso te lo aseguro!».
languages.original_text: "You see these corpses? These fine lads and lasses paid the price for my greed. And for your lies. We'll both be receiving the Emperor's punishment, of that you can be certain!"

traits.locale_text: «¿Ves estos cadáveres? Estos muchachos y muchachas han pagado el precio de mi avaricia. Y el de tus mentiras. A los dos nos llegará el castigo del Emperador, ¡eso te lo aseguro!».

languages.text: “看到那些尸体了吗？多么漂亮的小伙子、小姑娘！他们为我的贪念，为你的谎言付出了代价。咱们两个都会受到神皇的惩罚，我敢保证！”
languages.original_text: "You see these corpses? These fine lads and lasses paid the price for my greed. And for your lies. We'll both be receiving the Emperor's punishment, of that you can be certain!"

traits.locale_text: “看到那些尸体了吗？多么漂亮的小伙子、小姑娘！他们为我的贪念，还有你的谎言付出了代价。我们两人都会受到神皇的惩罚，我敢保证！”

languages.text: « Tu vois ces cadavres ? Ces braves jeunes gens ont payé pour ma cupidité et tes mensonges. On subira tous les deux le châtiment de l'Empereur, je te le promets ! »
languages.original_text: "You see these corpses? These fine lads and lasses paid the price for my greed. And for your lies. We'll both be receiving the Emperor's punishment, of that you can be certain!"

traits.locale_text: « Tu vois ces cadavres ? Ces braves jeunes gens ont payé pour ma cupidité et tes mensonges. On acceptera tous les deux le châtiment de l'Empereur, je te le promets ! »

languages.text: "Seht Ihr diese Leichen? Diese guten Männer und Frauen haben den Preis für meine Gier bezahlt. Und für Eure Lügen. Der Imperator wird uns beide strafen, darauf könnt Ihr Euch verlassen!"
languages.original_text: "You see these corpses? These fine lads and lasses paid the price for my greed. And for your lies. We'll both be receiving the Emperor's punishment, of that you can be certain!"

traits.locale_text: "Seht Ihr diese Leichen? Diese guten Männer und Frauen haben für meine Gier bezahlt. Und für Eure Lügen. Wir werden beide die Strafe des Imperators akzeptieren, darauf könnt Ihr Euch verlassen!"

languages.text: "O cesetleri görüyor musun? Ben açgözlüyüm, sen de yalancısın diye bedelini o güzel adamlarla kadınlar ödedi. Şüphen olmasın ki İmparator, ikimizi de cezalandıracak!"
languages.original_text: "You see these corpses? These fine lads and lasses paid the price for my greed. And for your lies. We'll both be receiving the Emperor's punishment, of that you can be certain!"
